WEBVTT

01:40:03.816 --> 01:40:05.691
Anyway, the police
know about it now, right?

01:40:05.774 --> 01:40:07.358
So go ahead
and file the complaint.

01:40:09.191 --> 01:40:10.774
It wouldn't be a good idea
for me to come there.

01:40:10.816 --> 01:40:12.566
-I'll send someone else.
-No need, sir.
